###
### Python Imaging Libraries
###
### Dependencies needed to compile Pillow (PIL), I recommend your own
### formulas use Pillow instead, i.e. 'pip install Pillow'
###

###
### Initialize
###

is_formula_installed && return || formula_init


###
### Installation
###

sudo apt-get -y install \
    libfreetype6-dev \
    libjpeg8-dev \
    liblcms1-dev \
    zlib1g-dev


###
### Teardown
###

formula_teardown
